title: Christine Wilson, Only Republican FTC Commissioner, Will Resign
description: Christine Wilson, the sole Republican commissioner at the F.T.C., criticized Lina Khan, the Democratic chair of the agency, accusing her of an “abuse of power.”

title: Combating Disinformation Wanes at Social Media Giants
description: As the companies have shed jobs recently, many teams assigned to combat false and misleading information have taken a hit.

title: The Changing Online Language of Hearts
description: How to show a heart — the universal symbol of love — has shifted on the internet over the years, driven by new technology.
